%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bosses%20are%20keeping%20tabs%20on%20their%20employees%20more%20than%20ever%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20camera%20surveils%20an%20employee%20who%20is%20playing%20games.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67af9ba46630eb10385cb9d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Chelsea%20Jia%20Feng%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBosses%20are%20increasingly%20watching%20what%20their%20employees%20are%20doing%20during%20the%20workday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDemand%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-companies-spy-on-employees-bossware-jpmorgan-amazon-monitor-rto-2023-10%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemployee%20surveillance%3C%2Fa%3E%20software%20rose%2054%25%20from%20March%202020%20to%20June%202023%2C%20a%20study%20found.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPressure%20is%20on%20for%20bosses%20to%20cut%20costs%20and%20root%20out%20unproductive%20workers%2C%20sources%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20reading%20this%20during%20your%20workday%2C%20there%20are%20pretty%20good%20odds%20that%20your%20boss%20knows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployers%20have%20monitored%20workers%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20but%20companies%20now%20have%20more%20sophisticated%20ways%20to%20watch%20what%20employees%20do%20while%20on%20the%20clock.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBosses%20are%20increasingly%20deploying%20tools%20that%20can%20track%20screen%20time%2C%20log%20keystrokes%2C%20and%20take%20videos%20and%20screenshots%20to%20keep%20tabs%20throughout%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20gadgets%2C%20which%20exploded%20in%20use%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-hybrid-jobs-rto-jpmorgan-amazon-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremote%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20off%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20are%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20workplace%20trend%20aimed%20at%20cutting%20costs%20and%20reducing%20head%20count%2C%20something%20execs%20think%20can%20be%20done%20more%20effectively%20by%20rooting%20out%20less%20productive%20workers%2C%20sources%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20March%202020%20and%20June%202023%2C%20demand%20for%20employee%20surveillance%20software%20grew%2054%25%2C%20according%20to%20research%20from%20Top10VPN%2C%20a%20virtual%20private%20network%20comparison%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%2073%25%20of%20employers%20said%20they%20used%20recordings%20of%20calls%2C%20emails%2C%20or%20other%20messages%20as%20a%20factor%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-leaders-track-manage-employee-performance-remotely%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperformance%3C%2Fa%3E%20reviews%2C%20while%2037%25%20said%20they%20used%20a%20recording%20to%20fire%20an%20employee%2C%20a%20separate%20survey%20from%20ExpressVPN%20study%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20employee%20monitoring%20software%20providers%20told%20Business%20Insider%20they%20had%20seen%20significant%20growth%20in%20the%20last%20year%2C%20with%20four%20of%20them%20reporting%20that%20they%20had%20scaled%20their%20clientele%20by%20more%20than%2025%25%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsightful%2C%20which%20makes%20monitoring%20software%20that%20allows%20employers%20to%20keep%20tabs%20on%20worker%20productivity%20through%20features%20like%20screenshotting%2C%20says%20it%20saw%20a%2045%25%20increase%20in%20customers%20last%20year.%20The%20firm%20is%20already%20on%20track%20to%20see%20its%20client%20base%20jump%20by%2070%25%20this%20year%2C%20Alexandra%20Alexin%2C%20Insightful's%20head%20of%20demand%20generation%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlexin%20attributed%20the%20increased%20interest%20to%20employers%20wanting%20to%20keep%20workers%20accountable%2C%20adding%20that%20some%20companies%20said%20they%20were%20looking%20to%20enforce%20certain%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20fantastic%20from%20a%20business%20perspective%2C%26quot%3B%20Alexin%20told%20BI%2C%20noting%20that%202024%20marked%20the%20company's%20best%20year%20on%20record.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20the%20real%20focus%20they%20have%20is%2C%20if%20those%20policies%20are%20being%20enforced%2C%20are%20they%20seeing%20more%20productivity%20and%20more%20efficiency%20from%20their%20workforce%20or%20not%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETime%20Doctor%2C%20another%20performance-tracking%20software%20firm%20that%20assigns%20productivity%20ratings%20and%20alerts%20employers%20of%20worker%20inactivity%2C%20said%20client%20interest%20increased%20by%20around%2050%25%20in%202024.%20Based%20on%20numbers%20over%20the%20last%20several%20quarters%2C%20the%20firm%20expects%20to%20see%20a%20similar%20increase%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiam%20Martin%2C%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Time%20Doctor%2C%20told%20BI%20he%20attributes%20the%20uptick%20in%20interest%20in%20employee%20monitoring%20tools%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20remote%20work%2C%20though%20cost-cutting%20has%20also%20come%20up%20in%20conversations%20with%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20single%20employer%20that%20I've%20spoken%20to%2C%20and%20I've%20asked%20them%2C%20'is%20your%20head%20count%20going%20to%20go%20down%20due%20to%20AI%3F'%20Pretty%20much%20everyone%20has%20said%20yes%2C%26quot%3B%20Martin%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20believed%20workers%20who%20were%20able%20to%20become%20more%20productive%20by%20using%20AI%20were%20not%20going%20to%20be%20let%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EControlio%2C%20an%20employee%20monitoring%20tool%20that%20can%20rank%20employees%20on%20a%20scale%20from%20%26quot%3BVery%20Productive%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3BVery%20Distracted%26quot%3B%20through%20features%20like%20keylogging%2C%20video%20recording%2C%20and%20surveying%20file%20activity%2C%20says%20it's%20seen%20a%2030%25%20increase%20in%20clients%20using%20its%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoath%20Galeb%2C%20an%20account%20manager%20at%20Controlio%2C%20said%20employers%20using%20Controlio%20are%20frequently%20shocked%20by%20how%20unproductive%20some%20employees%20are.%20He%20added%20that%20some%20employers%20have%20used%20the%20technology%20to%20determine%20which%20employees%20to%20let%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20our%20customers%20use%20it%20solely%20to%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20make%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecent-company-layoffs-laying-off-workers-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELayoff%3C%2Fa%3E%20announcements%20by%20companies%20rose%2028%25%20in%20January%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20from%20Challenger%2C%20Gray%20and%20Christmas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20third%20of%20business%20leaders%20said%20that%20reducing%20costs%20was%20their%20top%20priority%20in%202025%2C%20according%20to%20a%20survey%20conducted%20by%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group.%20Approximately%2086%25%20of%20executives%20said%20they%20planned%20on%20investing%20in%20AI%20or%20advanced%20analytics%20in%202025%2C%20BCG%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20employers%20may%20be%20flocking%20to%20such%20tools%2C%20workers%20are%20less%20enthused%20about%20the%20prospect%20of%20being%20monitored%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2056%25%20of%20workers%20who%20are%20monitored%20at%20work%20said%20they%20felt%20tense%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apa.org%2Ftopics%2Fhealthy-workplaces%2Femployee-electronic-monitoring%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estressed%3C%2Fa%3E%20out%2C%20according%20to%20the%20American%20Psychological%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETime%20Doctor's%20Martin%20says%20fewer%20employees%20push%20back%20against%20the%20technology%20once%20they%20understand%20how%20it%20works%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20believes%20the%20heightened%20transparency%20is%20necessary%20for%20remote%20work%20to%20succeed.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%2