had%20developed%20mechanisms%20for%20this%20and%20only%20the%20centre's%20nod%20remains%20for%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20current%20laws%20Indian%20citizens%20living%20abroad%20-%20for%20purpose%20of%20education%2C%20business%2C%20or%20employment%20-%20remain%20eligible%20to%20vote%20in%20this%20country%2C%20but%20must%20be%20physically%20present%20to%20do%20so%2C%20i.e.%2C%20they%20must%20travel%20to%20India%20to%20vote%20at%20designated%20booths.%20Since%202020%20the%20EC%20has%20been%20looking%20at%20alternate%20arrangements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20included%20voting%20by%20post%2C%20at%20Indian%20embassies%20or%20commissions%2C%20or%20online%2C%20but%20no%20concrete%20measure%20has%20been%20worked%20out%20so%20far%2C%20with%20political%20parties%20at%20odds%20over%20each%20of%20these%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20some%20estimates%20around%20one%20lakh%20NRIs%20are%20already%20registered%20to%20vote%2C%20with%20lakhs%20more%20eligible%20but%20not%20on%20the%20rolls.%20Around%2025%2C000%20of%20those%20registered%20came%20to%20India%20to%20vote%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20should%20take%20a%20final%20decision%20swiftly%20to%20enfranchise%20those%20who%20contribute%20significantly%20to%20our%20nation%20from%20afar%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20said%20on%20the%20'NRI%20voting%20from%20abroad'%20topic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsensus%20must%20also%20be%20developed%20on%20remote%20voting%20for%20migrant%20workers%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20EC%20Criticism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20speech%20Mr%20Kumar%20touched%20on%20several%20other%20issues%20too%2C%20including%20doubts%20over%20the%20EC's%20independence.%20Responding%20to%20that%20criticism%2C%20he%20slammed%20all%20%26quot%3Bmotivated%20and%20uncorroborated%20attacks%20on%20democratic%20institutions%26quot%3B%20and%20declared%20that%20these%20had%20not%20deterred%20the%20crores%20of%20India's%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20seemed%20to%20refer%20specifically%20to%20more%20recent%20allegations%20against%20the%20EC%20-%20from%20the%20Haryana%20and%20Maharashtra%20election%20in%20October%20last%20year%20and%20the%20Delhi%20election%20this%20month.%20In%20these%20polls%20-%20all%20three%20of%20which%20the%20BJP%20scored%20thumping%20wins%20-%20the%20opposition%20had%20questioned%20the%20speed%20and%20accuracy%20of%20voting%20data%2C%20trends%2C%20and%20results%20published%20by%20the%20poll%20body%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-to-congress-electoral-process-in-haryana-was-flawless-poll-body-hits-back-at-congress-6901438%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BHaryana%20Poll%20Process%20Was%20Flawless%26quot%3B%3A%20EC%20Snaps%20Back%20At%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20observed%20a%20pattern%20in%20the%20timing%20of%20certain%20narratives.%20During%20peak%20polling%20or%20counting%20hours%2C%20a%20wave%20of%20fake%20allegations%20and%20rumors%20begins%20to%20spread%20across%20media%20and%20social%20media%2C%20misleading%20people%20and%20creating%20confusion.%20Narratives%20are%20deliberately%20set%20to%20distort%20facts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20thundered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftactics-to-malign-poll-body-hits-back-at-aap-a-day-before-delhi-votes-7630521%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BTactics%20To%20Malign%26quot%3B%3A%20Poll%20Body%20Slams%20AAP%20Day%20Before%20Delhi%20Votes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20the%20Commission%20follows%20a%20policy%20of%20restraint%2C%20choosing%20not%20to%20respond%20while%20the%20election%20process%20is%20underway%2C%20ensuring%20that%20focus%20remains%20on%20the%20integrity%20and%20smooth%20conduct%2