0it%20took%20effort.%20I%20had%20to%20learn%20to%20respond%20instead%20of%20react%20to%20what%20was%20happening%20around%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20beauty%20of%20being%20committed%20to%20learning%3A%20you%20can%20always%20start%20over.%20I%20intentionally%20choose%20to%20parent%20differently%20every%20single%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22318b7461-41e6-4d94-a7e4-822df98bf618%5C%22%3EMy%20willingness%20to%20change%20and%20adapt%20paid%20off%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20I%20have%20a%20son%20who%20is%20eager%20to%20learn.%20He's%20willing%20to%20dig%20deeper%20without%20me%20asking%2C%20and%20I%20often%20find%20him%20starting%20lessons%20before%20I've%20gotten%20a%20chance%20to%20check%20his%20calendar%20for%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20think%20homeschooling%20would%20be%20my%20moment%20of%20humility%2C%20but%20I%20know%20I'll%20never%20regret%20what%20it%20taught%20me%20in%20those%20early%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%202%20years%20later%2C%20we%20are%20in%20a%20groove%20as%20a%20team.%20While%20I%20thought%20homeschooling%20would%20be%20temporary%2C%20we%20are%20both%20open%20to%20continuing%20as%20long%20as%20it%20works%20for%20both%20of%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20now%20understand%20my%20mothering%20is%20meant%20to%20empower%20my%20son%20in%20his%20own%20unique%20way%20by%20emphasizing%20his%20strengths%20%E2%80%94%20independence%20and%20confidence%20%E2%80%94%20over%20grade%20metrics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthought-i-knew-how-to-homeschool-son-strict-methods-backfired-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739790122000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ad13c8eb4be2fff9a47978%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthought-i-knew-how-to-homeschool-son-strict-methods-backfired-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Giana%20Vasconcellos%20thought%20sh