and%20Elon%20is%20going%20to%20work%20his%20magic.%20He%20seems%20to%20be%20very%20invested%20in%20making%20it%20a%20successful%20platform.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20marks%20a%20reversal%20from%20last%20year%20when%20he%20had%20little%20luck%20finding%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20nothing%2C%20literally%20zero%2C%20in%20all%20of%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20remembers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20buyers%20have%20been%20interested%20in%20purchasing%20shares%20at%20around%20the%20same%20price%20Musk%20paid%20in%202022%2C%20%2454.20-per-share%20at%20a%20%2444%20billion%20valuation%2C%20according%20to%20Anderson.%20It's%20worth%20noting%20that%20expressing%20interest%20in%20buying%20shares%20in%20the%20secondary%20market%20is%20a%20lot%20different%20than%20actually%20committing%20real%20money%20to%20a%20transaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFidelity%2C%20an%20investor%20in%20X%2C%20valued%20its%20shares%20of%20X%20at%20%2431-a-share%20at%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.actionsxchangerepository.fidelity.com%2FShowDocument%2FComplianceEnvelope.htm%3F_fax%3D-18%252342%2523-61%2523-110%2523114%252378%2523117%252320%2523-1%252396%252339%2523-62%2523-21%252386%2523-100%252337%252316%252335%2523-68%252391%2523-66%252354%2523103%2523-16%252369%2523-30%252358%2523-20%252376%2523-84%2523-11%2523-87%25230%2523-50%2523-20%2523-92%2523-98%2523-116%2523-28%252358%2523-38%2523-43%2523-39%2523-42%2523-96%2523-88%252388%2523-45%252336%252375%2523118%252350%2523-101%2523-95%2523116%252327%2523-74%25235%2523-89%2523-105%2523-67%2523126%252377%2523-126%2523-125%2523-107%252335%2523-105%2523-44%2523-41%2523-47%252365%252371%2523107%2523-82%2523-3%2523-86%2523-27%2523-57%2523-125%252342%2523119%252357%2523-111%252321%252363%2523-99%252317%2523-28%252320%2523-38%2523-101%2523113%252380%2523-77%2523-4%2523%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20recent%20disclosures%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20stock%20in%20public%20com