pace%20sector%20and%20pushing%20local%20firms%20to%20elevate%20their%20games%2C%20industry%20insiders%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengaluru-based%20Hical%20Technologies%20and%20JJG%20Aero%20are%20among%20those%20riding%20the%20wave.%20Hical%2C%20a%20supplier%20to%20Raytheon%20Technology%20and%20Boeing%20among%20others%2C%20aims%20to%20double%20revenue%20to%205%20billion%20rupees%20(%2457.57%20million)%20from%20its%20aerospace%20division%20in%20three%20years%2C%20said%20Yashas%20Jaiveer%20Shashikiran%2C%20joint%20managing%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJJG%20Aero%2C%20also%20in%20Bengaluru's%20industrial%20hub%2C%20took%2012%20years%20to%20hit%20%242%20million%20in%20revenue%20but%20soared%20to%20%2420%20million%20in%20the%20last%20six%2C%20said%20CEO%20Anuj%20Jhunjhunwala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20growth%20is%20part%20of%20an%20Indo-Pacific%20aerospace%20surge%2C%20with%202024%20revenue%20projected%20to%20be%2054%25%20above%202019%20levels%2C%20while%20North%20America%20and%20Europe%20remain%203%25%20and%204%25%20lower%2C%20according%20to%20Accenture%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%2C%20we%20were%20chasing%20customers.%20Now%2C%20they%20are%20equally%20interested%20in%20evaluating%20Indian%20machine%20shops%2C%26quot%3B%20Jhunjhunwala%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20contracts%20were%20being%20signed%20more%20quickly%20and%20onboarding%20processes%20being%20done%20much%20faster%20than%20ever%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20companies%20produce%20parts%20for%20landing%20gear%2C%20wings%2C%20fuselage%2C%20electrical%20switches%20and%20motion%20control%20systems%20essential%20for%20flight%20safety%20and%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeading%20Western%20plane%20and%20engine%20manufacturers%2C%20whose%20output%20has%20been%20constrained%20by%20strikes%2C%20production%20caps%2C%20and%20parts%20and%20labour%20shortages%20since%20the%20pandemic%2C%20say%20they%20want%20to%20source%20more%20from%20India%20to%20meet%20rising%20demand%20for%20air%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20the%20best%20solution%20to%20supply%20chain%20challenges%2C%26quot%3B%20Huw%20Morgan%2C%20senior%20vice%20president%20for%20aerospace%20procurement%20at%20Rolls-Royce%2C%20said%20last%20week%20at%20an%20industry%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20engine%20volumes%20are%20growing%20at%20around%2020%25%20and%20the%20traditional%20supply%20chains%20are%20just%20not%20able%20to%20support%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Morgan%20said.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20...%20the%20best%20cost%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20company%20plans%20to%20double%20sourcing%20from%20India%20within%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20is%20among%20the%20biggest%20aircraft%20buyers%20in%20the%20world%2C%20yet%20accounts%20for%20only%201%25%20of%20the%20global%20supply%20chain%20market%2C%20according%20to%20the%20recently%20formed%20Aerospace%20India%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPost-Covid%2C%20the%20global%20aerospace%20industry%20has%20reached%20an%20inflection%20point.%20While%20this%20shift%20began%20in%202020%2C%20aerospace%20is%20a%20slow-moving%20industry%20-%20it%20takes%20time%20for%20changes%20to%20materialise%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Aravind%20Melligeri%20of%20supplier%20Aequs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMORE%20PLANES%2C%20MORE%20PARTS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20the%20world's%20third-largest%20domestic%20aviation%20market%20by%20seats%2C%20is%20also%20among%20the%20fastest-growing%2C%20driving%20demand%20for%20maintenance%20services%20and%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMassive%20aircraft%20orders%20from%20IndiGo%20and%20Air%20India%20are%20fuelling%20growth%20across%20the%20aviation%20ecosystem%2C%20Air%20India%20CEO%20Campbell%20Wilson%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Indian%20firms%20have%20long%20supplied%20the%20%24180%20billion%20global%20aerospace%20industry%2C%20they%20are%20now%20moving%20beyond%20basic%20manufacturing%20to%20higher-value%20work%20such%20as%20design%2C%20engineering%2C%20and%20system%20integration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAirbus%20in%202024%20awarded%20its%20second%20aircraft%20door%20contract%20within%20a%20year%20to%20Indian%20suppliers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20contributing%20more%20than%201%20billion%20euros%20currently%20in%20the%20overall%20Airbus%20supply%20chain%20and%20we%20expect%20to%20double%20that.%20Every%20commercial%20aircraft%20of%20Airbus%20today%20has%20some%20part%20or%20component%20that%20is%20made%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Michel%20Narchi%2C%20head%20Of%20international%20operations%20at%20Airbus%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EINDUSTRY%20EFFORTS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20civil%20aviation%20ministry%20held%20a%20meeting%20last%20week%20with%20industry%20leaders%20about%20boosting%20component%20manufacturing%2C%20said%20AIA%20Director%20General%20Srinivasan%20Dwarakanath.%20The%20association%20represents%20both%20Indian%20and%20global%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20a%20key%20step%20towards%20real%20value%20addition%20would%20be%20the%20local%20sourcing%20of%20raw%20materials%20such%20as%20aluminium%2C%20steel%2C%20and%20titanium%2C%20eventually%20leading%20to%20certification%20of%20designs%20made%20by%20Indian%20suppliers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AIA%20estimates%20that%20India's%20aerospace%20industry%20will%20capture%2010%25%20of%20the%20global%20supply%20chain%20market%20within%20a%20decade%2C%20with%20the%20global%20market%20projected%20to%20reach%20%24250%20billion%20annually%20by%202033.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20also%20had%20the%20initial%20challenges%20of%20being%20physically%20farther%20away%20from%20the%20main%20markets%20of%20the%20U.S.%20and%20Europe.%20Engineering%20approvals%2C%20qualification%20timings%2C%20raw%20material%20sourcing%20-%20it%20took%20some%20time%20to%20build%20the%20ecosystem%2C%20but%20now%20India%20is%20all%20set%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hical's%20Yashas%20Jaivee