p%3E%26quot%3BThe%20RTO%20lever%20is%20the%20easy%20one%20to%20pull%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERemote%20or%20hybrid%20arrangements%20can%20give%20workers%20a%20stronger%20sense%20of%20autonomy%2C%20said%20Kyle%2C%20who%20is%20cofounder%20of%20CMP%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20is%20less%20engaging%20to%20employees%20than%20not%20having%20flexibility%20and%20choice%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2243d16f77-25f6-4d86-a249-61f576ba91b4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Predictable%20flexibility'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGinnie%20Carlier%2C%20Americas%20vice%20chair%20for%20talent%20at%20EY%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20firm's%20employees%20tend%20to%20work%20with%20their%20team%20leaders%20to%20plan%20days%20in%20the%20office%20%E2%80%94%20an%20approach%20she%20refers%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bpredictable%20flexibility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20one%20that's%20proven%20fruitful%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20most%20engaged%20and%20highest-performing%20individuals%20are%20the%20ones%20that%20are%20on%20a%20hybrid%20work%20arrangement%2C%26quot%3B%20Carlier%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20EY%20workers%2C%20that%20means%20spending%20two%20to%20three%20days%20a%20week%20in%20the%20office%2C%20she%20said.%20The%20focus%20is%20on%20how%20teams%20can%20work%20best%20together%2C%20not%20solely%20on%20how%20much%20gets%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20really%20gotten%20away%20from%20this%20discussion%20around%20this%20illusion%20of%20increased%20productivity%20by%20being%20in%20the%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20Carlier%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20when%20EY%20surveys%20new%20hires%20about%20why%20they%20accepted%20a%20job%20with%20the%20firm%2C%20flexibility%20reliably%20is%20one%20of%20the%20top%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudies%20from%20numerous%20settings%20show%20that%20giving%20people%20flexibility%20in%20how%20they%20work%20%E2%80%94%20and%20allowing%20them%20to%20work%2