naging%20director%20and%20private%20wealth%20advisor%20at%20Raymond%20James.%20Higher%20rates%20bring%20increased%20opportunities%20in%20fixed%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20anybody%20who%20wants%20to%20put%20money%20outside%20of%20the%20equity%20markets%2C%20higher%20for%20longer%20is%20a%20really%20good%20environment%20for%20that.%20High-yield%20savings%20accounts%2C%20money%20market%20accounts%2C%20CDs%2C%20even%20high-grade%20corporate%20bonds%20are%20paying%20a%20really%20attractive%20rate%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosner%20told%20BI.%20Savers%20or%20anyone%20with%20cash%20on%20the%20sidelines%20will%20benefit%20from%20higher%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20Zaccarelli%2C%20chief%20investment%20of%20Northlight%20Asset%20Management%2C%20recommends%3Cstrong%3E%20shorter-duration%20bonds%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20That's%20because%20bonds%20with%20a%20shorter%20duration%20are%20less%20exposed%20to%20interest%20rate%20risk%20and%20also%20offer%20attractive%20yields%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20have%20to%20go%20as%20far%20out%20the%20curve%20to%2010-year%2C%2020-year%2C%2030-year%20bonds%20or%20Treasurys%20in%20order%20to%20get%20higher%20yields.%20You%20can%20get%20quite%20a%20bit%20of%20yield%20in%20the%20shorter%20part%20of%20the%20yield%20curve%2C%26quot%3B%20Zaccarelli%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20that%20do%20want%20to%20stay%20in%20stocks%20in%20a%20high-rate%20environment%2C%20look%20for%20quality%2C%20Sl%C3%B8k%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20interest%20rates%20are%20higher%20for%20longer%2C%20companies%20with%20earnings%20tend%20to%20outperform%20because%20companies%20with%20earnings%20are%20able%20to%20pay%20higher%20debt%20servicing%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20Sl%C3%B8k%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDividend-paying%20stocks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20are%20also%20a%20good%20investment%20in%20times%20like%20these%2C%20according%20to%20Rosner.%20Companies%20that%20pay%20dividends%20are%20typically%20well-established%2C%20profitable%2C%20and%20have%20stable%20cash%20flows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinancials%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eare%20positioned%20to%20do%20well%2C%20too%2C%20said%20Chris%20Brigati%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer%20at%20investment%20firm%20SWBC.%20That's%20because%20he%20expects%20the%20yield%20curve%20to%20continue%20steepening%20as%20long-term%20Treasury%20rates%20creep%20higher.%20Banks%20borrow%20at%20the%20short-term%20rate%20and%20lend%20at%20the%20long-term%20rate%2C%20and%20higher%20interest%20rates%20will%20increase%20the%20amount%20banks%20earn%20on%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnergy%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20another%20sector%20that'll%20benefit%20from%20higher%20rates%2C%20both%20Brigati%20and%20Zaccarelli%20said.%20Energy%20and%20other%20commodities%20have%20historically%20performed%20well%20in%20higher%20rate%20and%20inflationary%20environments%2C%20according%20to%20Zaccarelli.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20in%20a%20business%20where%20you're%20selling%20a%20commodity%20and%20you%20can%20continue%20to%20provide%20that%20service%20or%20good%20at%20a%20continually%20higher%20price%20and%20consumers%20are%20forced%20to%20buy%20it%20at%20any%20price%2C%20then%20you're%20typically%20more%20insulated%20from%20inflation%2C%26quot%3B%20Zaccarelli%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20stay%20away%20from%20utilities%2C%20Zaccarelli%20warned%2C%20as%20the%20sector%20is%20inflation-sensitive.%20Utilities%20companies%20are%20also%20susceptible%20to%20interest-rate%20risk%20due%20to%20their%20capital-extensive%20business%20models%20and%20high%20debt%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20can%20get%20exposure%20to%20these%20trades%20through%20funds%20like%20the%20iShares%201-3%20Year%20Treasury%20Bond%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fishares-1-3-year-treasury-bond-etf-us4642874576%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESHY%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20the%20Financial%20Sele