n%20but%20he%20couldn't%20do%20that%20as%20the%20'other%20person'%20wasn't%20ready%20to%20talk.%20The%20veteran%20batter%20expected%20himself%20to%20be%20picked%20for%20India's%20next%20assignment%2C%20after%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20final%20in%202023%2C%20but%20was%20shown%20he%20door%2C%20without%20any%20explanation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20the%20person%20who%20will%20go%20and%20ask%20why%20I'm%20being%20dropped.%20There%20was%20no%20communication.%20Many%20said%20'go%20and%20talk'%20but%20one%20can%20only%20talk%20when%20the%20other%20person%20is%20ready%20to%20talk.%20If%20he%20is%20not%20ready%2C%20there%20is%20no%20point%20fighting.%20I%20wanted%20to%20talk%20one%20on%20one.%20I%20never%20messaged.%20I%20felt%20odd%20when%20I%20was%20dropped%20after%20the%20WTC%20final%20because%20I%20had%20worked%20hard%20for%20it.%20I%20thought%20I%20would%20be%20there%20for%20the%20next%20series.%20There%20is%20no%20point%20cribbing.%20I%20can%20only%20do%20what%20is%20in%20my%20hands.%20There%20is%20a%20belief%20that%20I%20will%20make%20a%20comeback%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2036-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlayers'%20PR%20teams%20also%20play%20a%20big%20role%20in%20creating%20fan%20pressure%20over%20selection%20or%20non-selection.%20Rahane%2C%20however%2C%20revealed%20that%20he%20doesn't%20have%20a%20PR%20team%20to%20push%20his%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20always%20shy%2C%20now%20I%20have%20opened%20up.%20My%20focus%20has%20been%20to%20play%20cricket%20and%20go%20home.%20Nobody%20told%20me%20that%20going%20ahead%2C%20certain%20things%20will%20be%20needed.%20Today%20also%2C%20sometimes%20I%20feel%20ki%20bas%20cricket%20khelo%2C%20ghar%20jao.%20Now%20I%20am%20told%20I%20need%20to%20speak%20up%2C%20talk%20about%20my%20hard%20work.%20People%20say%20you%20need%20to%20be%20in%20the%20news%20...%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20PR%20team%2C%20my%20only%20PR%20is%20my%20cricket.%20I%20have%20now%20realised%20that%20staying%20in%20the%20n