Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20escalating%20the%20school%20voucher%20debate.%3Cp%3EPhotoAlto%2FOdilon%20Dimier%2FGetty%2C%20sanjeri%2FGetty%2C%20Tyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20aimed%20at%20expanding%20school%20voucher%20programs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20escalated%20a%20state-level%20fight%20by%20proposing%20redirecting%20federal%20funds%20from%20public%20schools%20to%20private%20schools.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESupporters%20say%20vouchers%20give%20parents%20more%20choice%20in%20their%20kids'%20education%2C%20while%20skeptics%20say%20they%20sabotage%20public%20education.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20push%20to%20provide%20public%20money%20to%20parents%20to%20send%20their%20children%20to%20schools%20outside%20their%20district%20has%20been%20raging%20at%20the%20state%20level%20for%20years.%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20taking%20it%20up%20a%20notch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20recent%20executive%20order%20aimed%20at%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-school-choice-vouchers-education-policy-exeuctive-orders-anti-woke-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpanding%20school%20voucher%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehas%20long%20been%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-school-vouchers-arizona-cautionary-tale-savings-accounts-parents-cash-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epriority%20for%20Republican%20lawmakers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Trump's%20call%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epotentially%20redirect%20federal%20funds%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20that%20use%20would%20mark%20%26quot%3Ba%20huge%20ideological%20shift%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20conversation%2C%20said%20Derek%20Black%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20law%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20education%20at%20the%20University%20of%20South%20Carolina.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20federal%20government%2C%20since%20before%20we%20even%20had%20the%20United%20States%20Constitution%2C%20has%20put%20its%20weight%20behind%20trying%20to%20expand%20our%20public%20education%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20Black%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20called%20for%20federal%20agencies%20to%20determine%20whether%20they%20could%20redirect%20funding%20for%20states%20that%20receive%20federal%20block%20grants%20meant%20for%20public%20education%2C%20like%20the%20Child%20Care%20and%20Development%20Block%20Grant%2C%20to%20use%20instead%20for%20sending%20children%20to%20private%20and%20religious%20schools.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOver%2020%20states%20are%20already%20using%20their%20taxpayer%20funds%20for%20voucher%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvocates%20of%20vouchers%20lauded%20Trump's%20executive%20order%20for%20investing%20in%20more%20educational%20options%20and%20strengthening%20parents'%20role.%20Policy%20experts%20told%20BI%20that%20Trump's%20plan%20would%20likely%20face%20resistance%20from%20both%20Democratic%20and%20some%20Republican-led%20states%20that%20have%20previously%20rejected%20school%20voucher%20proposals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESavannah%20Newhouse%2C%20an%20Education%20Department%20spokesperson%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20administration%20believes%20in%20%26quot%3Binvesting%20in%20meaningful%20activities%20that%20help%20public%20schools%20deliver%20high-quality%20education.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinda%20McMahon%2C%20Trump's%20pick%20for%20education%20secretary%2C%20also%20said%20during%20her%20Thursday%20confirmation%20hearing%20that%20%26quot%3Bpublic%20schools%20are%20the%20bedrock%20of%20our%20education%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20universal%20vouchers%20will%20help%20public%20schools%20become%20more%20competitive.%20The%20administration%20has%20not%20yet%20introduced%20any%20proposals%20aimed%20at%20boosting%20public%20school%20education.%20Trump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20intended%20to%20ensure%20curricula%20in%20public%20classrooms%20align%20with%20his%20political%20ideologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlack%20said%20that%20diverting%20funding%20to%20private%20schools%2C%20by%20definition%2C%20%26quot%3Bmay%20very%20well%20hurt%20the%20public%20school%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221d91eefb-da36-414a-8649-fde7c5b4d235%5C%22%3EThe%20growth%20of%20the%20school-choice%20movement%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChristopher%20Lubienski%2C%20an%20education%20policy%20professor%20at%20Indiana%20University%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20idea%20that%20involving%20parents%20in%20their%20kids'%20educations%20would%20improve%20achievement%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edates%20back%20to%20the%20early%201990s.%20Now%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20focus%20is%20on%20providing%20more%20choices%20for%20students%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebeyond%20public%20school.%20The%20main%20criticism%20is%20that%20it%20could%20hurt%20students%20whose%20only%20option%20is%20public%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20the%20concern%20that%20families%20that%20don't%20have%20other%20options%20or%20can't%20get%20into%20a%20private%20school%20are%20going%20to%20be%20the%20ones%20left%20in%20public%20schools%2C%26quot%3B%20Lubienski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20US%20students%20go%20to%20public%20schools%2C%20many%20of%20which%20are%20supported%20by%20hefty%20local%20tax%20revenues%20in%20wealthy%20school%20districts.%20Lubienski%20said%20that%20families%20in%20rural%20areas%20with%20fewer%20school%20options%20rely%20more%20heavily%20on%20the%20federal%20block%20grants%20Trump%20is%20targeting%2C%20and%20that%20they%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewould%20suffer%20the%20most%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efrom%20funding%20diversions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20while%20voucher%20programs%20began%20with%20income%20thresholds%2C%20they%20have%20since%20morphed%20into%20universal%20programs%20in%20some%20states%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brookings.edu%2Farticles%2Farizonas-universal-education-savings-account-program-has-become-a-handout-to-the-wealthy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebenefiting%3C%2Fa%3E%20some%20more%20affluent%20families%20who%20would've%20sent%20their%20kids%20to%20private%20school%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESupporters%20of%20Trump's%20executive%20order%20said%20it's%20a%20step%20in%20the%20right%20direction%20for%20the%20US%20education%20system.%20Robert%20Enlow%2C%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20EdChoice%20%E2%80%94%20a%20nonprofit%20that%20advocates%20for%20voucher%20programs%20%E2%80%94%20told%20BI%20that%20Trump's%20executive%20order%20is%20intended%20to%20%26quot%3Bgive%20parents%20more%20power%20and%20to%20help%20states%20do%20their%20job%20better%2C%20rather%20than%20to%20get%20in%20the%20way%20of%20states.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnlow%20added%20that%20he%20thinks%20Trump's%20executive%20order%20will%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20students%20to%20directly%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eaccess%20federal%20funds%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethrough%20the%20block%20grants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20must%20it%20go%20through%20the%20federal%20government%20and%20then%20go%20through%20the%20state%20government%2C%20then%20go%20through%20local%20government%2C%20where%20everyone%20gets%20cuts%3F%20Why%20can't%20it%20be%20given%20directly%20to%20families%3F%20And%20I%20think%20that's%20what%20I%20really%20like%20about%20what%20he's%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20Enlow%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeri%20Rodrigues%2C%20cofounder%20and%20president%20of%20the%20National%20Parents%20Union%2C%20which%20advocates%20for%20policies%20that%20increase%20access%20to%20high-quality%20education%2C%20said%20that%20she's%20concerned%20about%20the%20potential%20outcome%20of%20redirecting%20public%20funds%20toward%20private%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20just%20push%20all%20this%20money%20down%20to%20the%20states%20and%20depend%20that%20they're%20going%20to%20make%20the%20right%20choices%20and%20do%20the%20right%20things%20without%20leadership%2C%20without%20standards%2C%20without%20guidance%20and%20direction%20and%20best%20practice%2C%26quot%3B%20Rodrigues%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20absurd.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286093a26-cc44-47e0-9010-dcc093e21400%5C%22%3EThe%20political%20limitations%20of%20Trump's%20plan%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELubieski%20said%20that%20Trump%20can%20only%20do%20so%20much%20without%20congressional%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20or%20not%20the%20White%20House%20goes%20through%20Congress%2C%20or%20they%20try%20to%20do%20this%20more%20through%20executive%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20Lubienski%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20allocating%20more%20federal%20funding%20toward%20school%20vouchers.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20a%20political%20strategy%20that%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20yet%20clear%20which%20one%20they're%20going%20to%20choose.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20only%20blue%20states%20that%20might%20be%20resistant%20to%20Trump's%20proposals.%20Voters%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsaz.com%2F2024%2F11%2F06%2Fkentucky-voters-reject-school-choice-ballot-measure%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKentucky%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnebraskaexaminer.com%2F2024%2F11%2F05%2Fnebraska-voters-reject-state-funding-for-students-attending-private-k-12-schools%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENebraska%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20two%20states%20that%20Trump%20won%20%E2%80%94%20rejected%20ballot%20measures%20that%20would%20have%20redirected%20funds%20from%20public%20schools%20to%20voucher%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlack%20said%20that%20if%20the%20Trump%20administration%20tries%20to%20allocate%20funds%20without%20congressional%20approval%2C%20there%20will%20likely%20be%20litigation.%20More%20broadly%2C%20he%20said%20the%20implications%20of%20prioritizing%20private%20and%20religious%20schools%20over%20public%20schools%20raise%20a%20red%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20premise%20of%20the%20public%20school%20system%2C%20going%20back%20to%20Jefferson%2C%20going%20back%20to%20John%20Adams%2C%20was%20it%20was%20the%20common%20ground%20upon%20which%20democracy%20would%20develop%2C%26quot%3B%20Black%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20you%20still%20have%20public%20schools%2C%20if%20people%20have%20one%20political%20stripe%2C%20or%20one%20religion%2C%20if%20they%20all%20leave%2C%20that%20ends%20up%20leaving%20the%20people%20of%20the%20other%20political%20stripes%20left%20alone%20in%20the%20public%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20problematic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGot%20a%20tip%2C%20or%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20securely%20on%20Signal%20at%20asheffey.97%20or%20email%20her%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3A%2520asheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-vouchers-school-choice-block-grants-public-funding-private-education-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739784962000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67af81de7bb3f854015cf585%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-vouchers-school-choice-block-grants-public-funding-private-education-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20aimed%20at%20expanding%20private%20school%20vouchers.%20Some%20education%20experts%20told%20BI%20it%20could%20put%20public%20schools%20at%20risk.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A43%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-vouchers-school-c