s%20now%20been%20summoned%20before%20the%20panel%20on%20March%206.%20Similarly%2C%20Apoorva%20Mukhija%20had%20expressed%20safety%20concerns%20and%20requested%20the%20panel%20to%20appear%20virtually.%20However%2C%20the%20panel%20denied%20her%20request%20and%20issued%20a%20fresh%20date%20of%20March%206%20to%20appear%20before%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamay%20Raina%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20on%20a%20pre-planned%20tour%20to%20the%20US%2C%20assured%20the%20commission%20that%20he%20will%20appear%20for%20a%20hearing%20once%20he%20returns%20to%20India.%20The%20commission%20accepted%20his%20request%20and%20rescheduled%20the%20hearing%20for%20March%2011.%20Comedian%20Jaspreet%20Singh%20is%20also%20on%20a%20pre-planned%20tour%20in%20Paris%20and%20will%20return%20by%20March%2010.%20He%20has%20also%20been%20asked%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20panel%20on%20March%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshish%20Chanchlani%2C%20whose%20lawyer%20appeared%20on%20his%20behalf%20citing%20illness%2C%20has%20been%20granted%20a%20rescheduled%20hearing%20on%20March%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProducer%20of%20the%20show%20'India's%20Got%20Latent'%2C%20Balraj%20Ghai%2C%20informed%20the%20commission%20that%20he%20is%20currently%20out%20of%20India%20and%20will%20respond%20once%20he%20returns.%20To%20this%2C%20the%20commission%20has%20rescheduled%20the%20hearing%20on%20March%2011.%20The%20other%20two%20producers%20-%20Tushar%20Poojari%20and%20Saurabh%20Bothra%20-%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20the%20summons%2C%20drawing%20condemnation%20from%20the%20panel.%20They%20have%20been%20summoned%20again%20to%20reappear%20on%20March%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Maharashtra%20Cyber%20Cell%20had%20asked%20Raina%20to%20record%20his%20statement%20in%20person%20on%20February%2018.%20However%2C%20since%20the%20YouTuber%20is%20on%20a%20tour%20in%20the%20US%2C%20he%20filed%20a%20petition%20saying%20he%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20return%20to%20India%20before%20March%2017.%20The%20Cyber%20Cell%20has%20refused%20the%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'India's%20Got%20Latent'%20row%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20huge%20row%20broke%20out%20after%20YouTuber%20and%20podcaster%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%2C%20known%20as%20'BeerBiceps'%2C%20made%20distasteful%20comments%20about%20parents%20and%20sex%20on%20Raina's%20show%20'India's%20Got%20Latent'.%20The%20remarks%20sparked%20massive%20outrage%2C%20leading%20to%20multiple%20complaints%20against%20the%20social%20media%20personality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20teams%20of%20Mumbai%20and%20Assam%20police%20visited%20Allahbadia's%20home%20to%20record%20his%20statement%2C%20but%20they%20found%20it%20locked.%20A%20day%20later%2C%20Allahbadia%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20social%20media%20saying%20he%20has%20been%20cooperating%20with%20the%20police%20and%20all%20other%20authorities%20and%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20available%20to%20all%20the%20agencies%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20mentioned%20that%20he%20has%20been%20getting%20death%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaina%20also%20issued%20a%20statement%20saying%20he%20had%20removed%20all%20videos%20of%20the%20show%20from%20his%20channel%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bfully%20cooperating%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20authorities.%20%26quot%3BEverything%20that%20has%20been%20happening%20has%20been%20too%20much%20for%20me%20to%20handle.%20I%20have%20removed%20all%20India's%20Got%20Latent%20videos%20from%20my%20channel.%20My%20only%20objective%20was%20to%20make%20people%20laugh%20and%20have%20a%20good%20time.%20I%20will%20fully%20cooperate%20with%20all%20agencies%20to%20ensure%20their%20inquiries%20are%20concluded%20fairly.%20Thank%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739783940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fdh0liip8_ranveer-allahbadia-samay-raina_625x300_10_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsamay-raina-ranveer-allahbadia-fail-to-appear-before-womens-body-summoned-ag