Here%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENew%20FASTag%20regulations%20came%20into%20force%20from%20today.%20The%20FASTag%20payments%20will%20now%20be%20verified%20within%20a%20designated%20time%20frame%20from%20the%20moment%20the%20tag%20is%20scanned%20at%20a%20toll%20plaza%2C%20the%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(NPCI)%20said%20in%20a%20circular%20dated%20January%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20FASTag%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFASTag%20is%20an%20electronic%20toll%20collection%20system%20which%20allows%20cashless%20payments%20at%20toll%20plazas.%20It%20uses%20Radio%20Frequency%20Identification%20(RFID)%20technology%20to%20automatically%20deduct%20toll%20charges%20from%20a%20linked%20bank%20account%2C%20prepaid%20wallet%2C%20or%20payment%20app.%20A%20FASTag%20sticker%20is%20affixed%20to%20the%20vehicle's%20windshield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20vehicle%20approaches%20a%20toll%20booth%2C%20RFID%20sensors%20scan%20the%20tag%20and%20charge%20the%20linked%20account.%20The%20barrier%20then%20opens%2C%20allowing%20the%20vehicle%20to%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChanges%20in%20FASTag%20Rules%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlacklisted%20FASTags%20-%20No%20Transactions%20Allowed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20a%20FASTag%20is%20blacklisted%2C%20placed%20on%20a%20hotlist%2C%20or%20marked%20as%20low%20balance%20for%20more%20than%2060%20minutes%20before%20reaching%20the%20toll%20booth%2C%20the%20transaction%20will%20be%20declined.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20a%20FASTag%20remains%20blacklisted%20for%2010%20minutes%20after%20being%20scanned%2C%20the%20payment%20will%20also%20be%20rejected.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20both%20conditions%20are%20met%2C%20the%20system%20will%20decline%20the%20transaction%20with%20error%20code%20176%2C%20and%20the%20vehicle%20will%20be%20charged%20double%20the%20toll%20fee%20as%20a%20penalty.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrace%20Period%20